        <icon>icon.png</icon>
        <description>Guilded objects for Guilded.NET</description>
        <releaseNotes>
- Profile related things
- Small and large heading, divider nodes
- Content created and removed events
- Media, docs(no doc replies and no way to get a document from the channel), forum posts, forum replies
- Role permission channel ID error fix
